{"tid":690708,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"六四優先座","createTime":"2018-06-05T05:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T05:34:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb94ce1d6badf9a4142354dcda3eb0eb1cd6cae","tid":690708,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180605/20410840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F20410840&d=ReI%2BzhX26GbyCeZBK3HxHfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=481a263f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F20410840&h=cb7babef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20180605/20410840</a><br />\n<br />\n六四優先座<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180605/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180605%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=0ae0910e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n六月四，全世界都冇的敏感詞，只在強國出現？<br />\n<br />\n噢不，香港也爆發六月恐懼症，雅虎選擇性死機，頁面報喪：我們找不到「八九六四」的結果。<br />\n<br />\n64廿九年，結出這樣的果，網站大可以理直氣壯表態，年輕人都唔關注八九六四啦，零搜尋啊。六月四抑或五月三十五號，對年輕人而言，不是「鄰國發生的事，無義務去平反，無責任去悼念」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n網站找年輕人過橋，圍封六四有青春無敵的理由。睇唔到，搵唔到，即係唔重要，事不關己lol。六四資訊被網站屏蔽，機不離手的後生一代，頭也不回，輕鬆滑機，遺忘，找到理所當然的擋箭牌。<br />\n<br />\n年輕人缺席嗎？沒有後生仔爭坐六四優先座，老餅平靜就位，拖住老而不化的軀殼，裹住哀傷的心，緩緩往維園開動。展示六四傷痕的夜晚，形形種種的人心，千古不移的燭光追悼，行禮如儀的大台治療，29年了，你仍未找到「結果」。這樣，在終結悲傷依舊無期的每個六月四，老友，自動波，維園有落。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「伙記．埋單！」 (尊子)"}]}